This map was started in 2008 by Chrisber and me, sea212. We had almost finished that map, but for some reason this map was abandoned. The last time we edited this map was february 2009. Since then, this map was just laying around on my hard drive. Today I found it and after checking it out again I decided to publish it before it gets lost.
this map is incomplete (although it got 8 stages)

have fun!
